OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F312A1776146706
OL,3,CWhy is Trump blocking Iran's ports,
OL,4,Cand could this drive up oil prices?
OL,6,FBy ITV News Producer James Hockaday
OL,8,FThe US military has announced it has
OL,9,Fbegun a blockade of all Iranian ports
OL,10,Fand coastal areas as Donald Trump's
OL,11,Fadministration continues to grapple
OL,12,Fwith Iran's effective closure of the
OL,13,FStrait of Hormuz.
OL,15,FThroughout the current conflict, Iran
OL,16,Fhas insisted the crucial shipping
OL,17,Fchannel is open to all except for the
OL,18,FUnited States and its allies, but
OL,19,Fmaritime data shows traffic has fallen
OL,20,Fsharply since the war began.
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G1/20
OL,2,W/*%+,"-/.!,.!T,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BNat News CNat TV FClean Feed
FL,313,300,200,140,000,100
PN,31202
SC,0002
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F312A1776146706
OL,3,CWhy is Trump blocking Iran's ports,
OL,4,Cand could this drive up oil prices?
OL,6,FDespite the military strength of the
OL,7,FUS and Israel, the Strait of Hormuz
OL,8,Fhas proven to be a major thorn in
OL,9,FTrump's side, who is now seeking to
OL,10,Fincrease pressure on Tehran with a
OL,11,Fshipping blockade of his own.
OL,13,FThe US blockage cames after
OL,14,Fnegotiations between Iran and the US
OL,15,Fin Pakistan failed to reach an
OL,16,Foutcome, due to disagreements over
OL,17,FTehran's nuclear programme, according
OL,18,Fto US vice-president JD Vance.
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G2/20
OL,2,W/*%+,"-/.!,.!T,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BNat News CNat TV FClean Feed
FL,313,300,200,140,000,100
PN,31203
SC,0003
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F312A1776146706
OL,3,CWhy is Trump blocking Iran's ports,
OL,4,Cand could this drive up oil prices?
OL,6,FIn the wake of Sunday's failed talks,
OL,7,FTrump announced on his Truth Social
OL,8,Fplatform that the US Navy would "begin
OL,9,Fthe process of BLOCKADING any and all
OL,10,FShips trying to enter, or leave, the
OL,11,FStrait of Hormuz".
OL,13,FHe has since appeared to have rowed
OL,14,Fback on this threat slightly, instead
OL,15,Fvowing a targeted blockade of ships
OL,16,Fcoming in and out of Iranian ports.
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G3/20
OL,2,W/*%+,"-/.!,.!T,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BNat News CNat TV FClean Feed
FL,313,300,200,140,000,100
PN,31204
SC,0004
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F312A1776146706
OL,3,CWhy is Trump blocking Iran's ports,
OL,4,Cand could this drive up oil prices?
OL,6,FThis, along with a retaliatory threat
OL,7,Fby Iran on all ports in the Persian
OL,8,FGulf and Gulf of Oman, threatens to
OL,9,Fdrive oil prices even further while
OL,10,Fpotentially reigniting the war
OL,11,Fcurrently halted by a fragile
OL,12,Fceasefire.
OL,14,FWhy is Trump imposing a blockade on
OL,15,FIranian ports?
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G4/20
OL,2,W/*%+,"-/.!,.!T,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BNat News CNat TV FClean Feed
FL,313,300,200,140,000,100
PN,31205
SC,0005
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F312A1776146706
OL,3,CWhy is Trump blocking Iran's ports,
OL,4,Cand could this drive up oil prices?
OL,6,FThe combined threat of sea mines and
OL,7,Fpossible attacks from Iran's
OL,8,Fparamilitary Revolutionary Guard has
OL,9,Fkept ships away from the Strait of
OL,10,FHormuz, in effect closing the crucial
OL,11,Fwaterway through which about one-fifth
OL,12,Fof the world's oil travels.
OL,14,FTrump is furious with Tehran for using
OL,15,Fits economic leverage in this way and
OL,16,Fincreasingly frustrated at US allies,
OL,17,Fincluding the UK, resolving to stay
OL,18,Fout of the conflict.
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G5/20
OL,2,W/*%+,"-/.!,.!T,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BNat News CNat TV FClean Feed
FL,313,300,200,140,000,100
PN,31206
SC,0006
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F312A1776146706
OL,3,CWhy is Trump blocking Iran's ports,
OL,4,Cand could this drive up oil prices?
OL,6,FDr Rob Geist Pinfold, a lecturer in
OL,7,Finternational security at King's
OL,8,FCollege London, told ITV News that
OL,9,FWashington appeared to have
OL,10,Funderestimated Tehran's willingness to
OL,11,Fuse the strait as a strategic weapon.
OL,13,F"If it (the US) was prepared... It
OL,14,Fwould have brought things like anti-
OL,15,Fmining vessels, for example, or
OL,16,Finfantry units with amphibious
OL,17,Fcapabilities like marines," he told
OL,18,FITV News.
OL,26,@uD@HpmuD@Opn
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G6/20
OL,2,W/*%+,"-/.!,.!T,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BNat News CNat TV FClean Feed
FL,313,300,200,140,000,100
PN,31207
SC,0007
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F312A1776146706
OL,3,CWhy is Trump blocking Iran's ports,
OL,4,Cand could this drive up oil prices?
OL,6,FNow, Trump is hoping to turn Iran's
OL,7,Fstrategy back on itself and force
OL,8,FTehran's hand by blocking Iran's oil
OL,9,Fexports, Dr Pinfold said.
OL,11,F"Obviously Iran is using the Strait of
OL,12,FHormuz as a bargaining chip and it's a
OL,13,Fkey economic and military flashpoint
OL,14,Fin this conflict," he told ITV News.
OL,16,F"So what Trump is trying to do is
OL,17,Fbasically turn it around and say,
OL,18,F'look, you know, we can also use this
OL,19,Ftoo. We can blockade the Strait of
OL,20,FHormuz too, and put the squeeze on
OL,21,FIran'.
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G7/20
OL,2,W/*%+,"-/.!,.!T,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BNat News CNat TV FClean Feed
FL,313,300,200,140,000,100
PN,31208
SC,0008
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F312A1776146706
OL,3,CWhy is Trump blocking Iran's ports,
OL,4,Cand could this drive up oil prices?
OL,6,F"During the recent conflict, an
OL,7,Festimated 60% of the ships that were
OL,8,Fpassing through the Strait of Hormuz
OL,9,Fwere going to Iran or were Iranian-
OL,10,Fflagged."
OL,12,FHe added: "The Americans are trying to
OL,13,Fuse this as a way to get a better deal
OL,14,Fin the talks."
OL,16,FBy blocking Iranian oil exports, Trump
OL,17,Fcould cut off a crucial source of
OL,18,Ffunding for Iran's government and
OL,19,Fmilitary operations, but his plan is
OL,20,Ffraught with risks, both military and
OL,21,Feconomic.
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G8/20
OL,2,W/*%+,"-/.!,.!T,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BNat News CNat TV FClean Feed
FL,313,300,200,140,000,100
PN,31209
SC,0009
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F312A1776146706
OL,3,CWhy is Trump blocking Iran's ports,
OL,4,Cand could this drive up oil prices?
OL,6,FDr Pinfold explained: "The question is
OL,7,Fhow Iran sees this and how it responds
OL,8,Fin kind. Are we going to see some
OL,9,Flimited retaliation or are we going to
OL,10,Fend up going back up the escalation
OL,11,Fladder quite quickly in the ceasefire
OL,12,Fbreaking down? It's a very, very high-
OL,13,Frisk tactic."
OL,15,FHow difficult would a US-led blockade
OL,16,Fbe?
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G9/20
OL,2,W/*%+,"-/.!,.!T,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BNat News CNat TV FClean Feed
FL,313,300,200,140,000,100
PN,31210
SC,0010
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F312A1776146706
OL,3,CWhy is Trump blocking Iran's ports,
OL,4,Cand could this drive up oil prices?
OL,6,FDr Pinfold said such an operation
OL,7,Fwould be "very, very difficult" as it
OL,8,Fwould mean putting sailors in the
OL,9,FStrait of Hormuz "in harm's way",
OL,10,Ffaced with "multi-layered" Iranian
OL,11,Fthreats.
OL,13,F"We know now that most of the
OL,14,FRevolutionary Guard's boats used to
OL,15,Fblockade or create havoc in the
OL,16,Fstraits are intact, so Iran has the
OL,17,Fnaval capacity to do that. It also has
OL,18,Fdrones and missiles as well.
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                   G10/20
OL,2,W/*%+,"-/.!,.!T,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BNat News CNat TV FClean Feed
FL,313,300,200,140,000,100
PN,31211
SC,0011
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F312A1776146706
OL,3,CWhy is Trump blocking Iran's ports,
OL,4,Cand could this drive up oil prices?
OL,6,F"This is something that the US can
OL,7,Fdeal with, but the question is what's
OL,8,Ftheir threshold for pain? If Iran
OL,9,Fstarts attacking and there are US
OL,10,Fcasualties, who blinks first?
OL,12,F"I think the Iranians are banking on
OL,13,Fbeing able to cause enough damage for
OL,14,Fthe US to basically not think this is
OL,15,Fa viable strategy. So it is on paper
OL,16,Fdoable, but the question is what price
OL,17,Fis the US willing to pay to achieve
OL,18,Fit?"
OL,20,FWhat impact will it have on oil prices?
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                   G11/20
OL,2,W/*%+,"-/.!,.!T,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BNat News CNat TV FClean Feed
FL,313,300,200,140,000,100
PN,31212
SC,0012
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F312A1776146706
OL,3,CWhy is Trump blocking Iran's ports,
OL,4,Cand could this drive up oil prices?
OL,6,FA US blockade will inevitably cause
OL,7,Ffurther economic pain in the short
OL,8,Fterm, experts say.
OL,10,FUS Oil prices climbed on Monday after
OL,11,Fthe US military said it would
OL,12,Fimplement the shipping blockade. Brent
OL,13,Fcrude, the global oil benchmark, rose
OL,14,F7% to near $102 a barrel ` a gain of
OL,15,F40% since the start of the war.
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                   G12/20
OL,2,W/*%+,"-/.!,.!T,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BNat News CNat TV FClean Feed
FL,313,300,200,140,000,100
PN,31213
SC,0013
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F312A1776146706
OL,3,CWhy is Trump blocking Iran's ports,
OL,4,Cand could this drive up oil prices?
OL,6,FPetras Katinas, research fellow in
OL,7,Fclimate, energy and defence at the
OL,8,FRoyal United Services Institute
OL,9,F(RUSI), told ITV News that oil prices
OL,10,Fare rising not because supply has
OL,11,Fcollapsed, but because markets fear it
OL,12,Fmight, and that fear alone is enough
OL,13,Fto push costs up.
OL,15,F"This is not really about a sudden
OL,16,Floss of supply. It is a risk shock.
OL,17,FThe fact that only a small number of
OL,18,Fvessels are currently moving through
OL,19,Fthe Strait is exactly what is driving
OL,20,Fprices higher," he explained.
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                   G13/20
OL,2,W/*%+,"-/.!,.!T,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BNat News CNat TV FClean Feed
FL,313,300,200,140,000,100
PN,31214
SC,0014
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F312A1776146706
OL,3,CWhy is Trump blocking Iran's ports,
OL,4,Cand could this drive up oil prices?
OL,6,F"Traders are pricing in uncertainty,
OL,7,Fwhether those flows continue at all,
OL,8,Fwho controls them, and how quickly the
OL,9,Fsituation could escalate.
OL,11,F"Fuel prices were already rising, and
OL,12,Fthis will add further pressure at the
OL,13,Fpump and on transport costs. So, the
OL,14,Fimpact people feel is not empty petrol
OL,15,Fstations, but steadily rising costs
OL,16,Facross energy and the wider economy."
OL,18,FEven Trump mentioning the Strait of
OL,19,FHormuz "tends to create reverberations
OL,20,Fthroughout the markets", Dr Pinfold
OL,21,Fsaid.
OL,26,@xD@eO]
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                   G14/20
OL,2,W/*%+,"-/.!,.!T,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BNat News CNat TV FClean Feed
FL,313,300,200,140,000,100
PN,31215
SC,0015
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F312A1776146706
OL,3,CWhy is Trump blocking Iran's ports,
OL,4,Cand could this drive up oil prices?
OL,6,F"I think Trump is banking on high risk
OL,7,Fstrategy and is trying to get Iran to
OL,8,Fback down sooner rather than later.
OL,10,F"He knows this is not sustainable. But
OL,11,FI think there's a hope that the US can
OL,12,Fforce Iran's hand by doing exactly
OL,13,Fwhat Iran has been doing to the global
OL,14,Feconomy, to Iran."
OL,16,FWhat is the UK's involvement?
OL,18,FTrump is angry at allies for ignoring
OL,19,Fhis call to help reopen the Strait of
OL,20,FHormuz, with Keir Starmer particularly
OL,21,Fsingled out by the president.
OL,26,@vD@RO]
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                   G15/20
OL,2,W/*%+,"-/.!,.!T,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BNat News CNat TV FClean Feed
FL,313,300,200,140,000,100
PN,31216
SC,0016
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F312A1776146706
OL,3,CWhy is Trump blocking Iran's ports,
OL,4,Cand could this drive up oil prices?
OL,6,FDespite the repeated White House
OL,7,Finsults, the prime minister repeated
OL,8,Fhis assertion that the UK would not
OL,9,Fget dragged into the Iran war as he
OL,10,Frefused to support Trump's proposed
OL,11,Fblockade in the Strait of Hormuz.
OL,13,FThe UK has deployed minesweepers and
OL,14,Fanti-drone capabilities to the region,
OL,15,Fbut Dr Pinfold said it was likely
OL,16,FBritish forces were already doing this
OL,17,Findependently of Trump's blockade
OL,18,Fplans.
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                   G16/20
OL,2,W/*%+,"-/.!,.!T,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BNat News CNat TV FClean Feed
FL,313,300,200,140,000,100
PN,31217
SC,0017
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F312A1776146706
OL,3,CWhy is Trump blocking Iran's ports,
OL,4,Cand could this drive up oil prices?
OL,6,FDr Pinfold said that the US was not
OL,7,Fprepared for the Strait to play such a
OL,8,Fdecisive part in the war and is now
OL,9,Fscrabbling to address the problem,
OL,10,Fincluding pressuring other Nato
OL,11,Fcountries to step in.
OL,13,FSubscribe free to our weekly
OL,14,Fnewsletter for exclusive and original
OL,15,Fcoverage from ITV News. Direct to your
OL,16,Finbox every Friday morning.
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                   G17/20
OL,2,W/*%+,"-/.!,.!T,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BNat News CNat TV FClean Feed
FL,313,300,200,140,000,100
PN,31218
SC,0018
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F312A1776146706
OL,3,CWhy is Trump blocking Iran's ports,
OL,4,Cand could this drive up oil prices?
OL,6,F"Trump is trying to lean on other
OL,7,Fcountries, particularly Nato allies,
OL,8,Fbut also the UAE and others, to
OL,9,Fbasically act as a force multiplier,
OL,10,Fto plug the gap.
OL,12,F"My understanding is that the UK is
OL,13,Fcurrently involved in clearing mines,
OL,14,Fbut they are trying to do this
OL,15,Findependently of whatever Trump's
OL,16,Fblockade plan is."
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                   G18/20
OL,2,W/*%+,"-/.!,.!T,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BNat News CNat TV FClean Feed
FL,313,300,200,140,000,100
PN,31219
SC,0019
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F312A1776146706
OL,3,CWhy is Trump blocking Iran's ports,
OL,4,Cand could this drive up oil prices?
OL,6,FDr Pinfold argues this is a "pretty
OL,7,Fright balancing act", as a potential
OL,8,FIranian response, "or at least a
OL,9,Fstandoff", could mean other parties
OL,10,Fgetting "caught in the crossfire".
OL,12,F"So if Trump does carry out this
OL,13,Fthreat, I think the UK's current
OL,14,Fcourse is going to be pretty
OL,15,Funsustainable."
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                   G19/20
OL,2,W/*%+,"-/.!,.!T,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
